import zIndex from '@material-ui/core/styles/zIndex'
import {makeStyles} from '@material-ui/styles'

const useStyles = makeStyles((theme)=>({
   box:{
      position:'absolute',
      top:'0',
      left:'0',
      right:'0',
      bottom:'0',
      height:'100%',
      width:'100%',
      overFlow:'hidden',
      zIndex:'1'
   },
  
   video:{
       width:"100%",
       height:'100%',
       oobjectFit:'cover',
       objectFit:'cover',
    zIndex:'-1'
   },
  
}))

export default useStyles
